The '''''Laughing Sullustan''''' was a [[Starship/Legends|starship]] attached to the mysterious [[Space station/Legends|space station]] called [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']], where it was located in [[Sector Delta]].<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

Originally, it was owned by a [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lord]] named [[Quentin Bartog]]. After Bartog had disappeared along with all other lifeforms when the station mysteriously vanished and reappeared, the ''Laughing Sullustan'' was taken over by a group of riffraff and criminals, calling themselves the [[Bartog Syndicate]] under the leadership of [[Ace of Staves (individual)|Ace of Staves]].<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)" />

The ''Laughing Sullustan'' was a custom-built deluxe vessel which boasted some of the most comfortable accommodations. By the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] most of the luxurious interior had been stripped away by thieves.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)" />

